description:
The Free Planets Alliance battleship Lugeilan was flagship of the Free Planets Alliance 5th Fleet under the command of Vice Admiral Wallace Warwick. Pennant number 0501.
In the mythology of some of the peoples of the Caroline Island Lugeilan is the god of knowledge. He descended from heaven to earth and taught the people how to cultivate crops and the arts of tattooing and hairdressing. Lugeilan is associated with the coconut palm. His son is the god of change Olofat.
